text:
...You know, White Day return gifts,
they often carry quite a bit of meaning, don't they?

So, like... even if you want to give something you find
delicious, you might get stopped along the way.
It's indeed quite challenging to navigate...

...Yeah.
I really understand how you feel.
Receiving unintended feelings can be disheartening.

Yeah!
I'm glad you understand... That's my strategy!
For White Day from me, it's going to be a taste showdown!
